# 6. Type Conversion Evaluation

### Source Type

```mlir id="mlgjvx"
tensor<?x?xf32>
```

### Target Type

```mlir id="5qf12r"
memref<?x?xf32>
```

Result:

PASS

All tensor types were successfully converted to MemRef types without loss of shape or element information.

