# 11. Conclusion

The evaluation demonstrates that the MdArray dialect and its lowering pass function correctly and satisfy all project requirements. All custom tensor operations were successfully lowered to MemRef-based operations, verification checks worked as expected, and the resulting IR contained only legal target dialect operations. The project effectively showcases MLIR's progressive lowering methodology and validates the advantages of dialect-based compiler design.
